{"tid":879591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極右「巴西特朗普」勢贏今大選","createTime":"2018-10-28T05:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T07:43:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2589b9e1ff6ba31f13ae040965f8dc957114d41c","tid":879591,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181028/20532610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181028%2F20532610&d=IT0WKWL4evWOYlI9S0Ou9Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4bb36ee4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181028%2F20532610&h=1c0751e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181028/20532610</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月28日 <br />\n<br />\n極右「巴西特朗普」勢贏今大選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181028/large/28wx7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181028%2Flarge%2F28wx7p.jpg&h=ee621b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n里約熱內盧選舉法庭外的示威者展示反對法西斯主義的橫幅。法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統選舉今日舉行次輪投票，預料有「巴西特朗普」之稱的極右候選人博爾索納羅（Jair Bolsonaro）將勝出。選前民調顯示，他以56%的支持率力壓主要對手、工人黨左翼候選人阿達的44%。<br />\n<br />\n本月初的首輪投票中，博爾索納羅得票率為46%，拋離阿達的29%，分析指他只要穩定原有票倉並集中爭取游離票便可穩勝。勝出者將於明年1月1日接任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉以非法資金唱衰對手<br />\n<br />\n63歲的博爾索納羅主張鐵腕執政，如擴充警權打擊罪案和放寬槍管。擅用社交媒體宣傳的他近日爆出醜聞，有報章指他涉以未經申報的資金聘五毛黨，在WhatsApp散佈假消息唱衰對手。他否認指控，威脅當選後不會在該報落廣告。<br />\n<br />\n選舉法庭已展開調查，若使用非法資金競選罪成，候選人可被褫奪參選資格。但法庭的公正性遭質疑，前日過千名民眾到里約熱內盧選舉法庭外示威，抗議法庭頒令大學拆除「非法政治宣傳」的橫額，如寫有「法律系學生反法西斯主義」和支持維權人士的橫額，惹來法庭打壓言論自由的批評。<br />\n<br />\n多國前領袖聯署聲明「反巴西法西斯」，譴責他「仇外、種族歧視和恐同」。55歲的阿達雖形容自己是民主救星，但擺脫不了工人黨前總統盧拉的貪腐醜聞困擾，加上工人黨執政13年為人詬病，選民求變心切，使他難以扭轉劣勢。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美猶太教堂外爆槍戰8死3警傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n與戴妃不合　查理斯想過取消婚禮"},{"pid":"395c0d4068c55752d70c97cbf4b3948540e0169a","tid":879591,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"Make Brazil great again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12da429594b488aaf685a97c2b532781c398d913","tid":879591,"uid":22913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"395c0d4068c55752d70c97cbf4b3948540e0169a","tid":879591,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"Make Brazil great again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"無great過"},{"pid":"a0094660b5d26c9b1da58fd2e0892d46825bf0e2","tid":879591,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"支那買大豆有難"},{"pid":"f0e47c4919b03e2216c11ae9d69b34e72d4af4a5","tid":879591,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"聽聞佢好親台<br />\n想跟台建交"},{"pid":"3668b3806a8029aebc80f0716f454b9a9b5d62c7","tid":879591,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"QAnon又中"},{"pid":"0924bdd7b0890fb0f66ff5d0c6b7f5ef02604fa1","tid":879591,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0094660b5d26c9b1da58fd2e0892d46825bf0e2","tid":879591,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"支那買大豆有難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"何解？咁大筆生意<br />\n<br />\n佢話過當選後親美？"},{"pid":"583b7d4f0ecc4dafdda8637663de27759fee7885","tid":879591,"uid":213597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a1d4926f8f5a529670c22f189452b6c4c3f35ca","tid":879591,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"